<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include("partials/head") %>
</head>
<body>
<header>
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center m-5">
        <img id="logo" src="public/img/LSS-Logo.png" alt="LSS Logo">
    </div>
</header>
<nav class="py-4 sticky-top">
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-evenly align-items-center container">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
        <div class="dropdown">
            <a class="dropbtn">Resources</a>
            <div class="dpdn-content px-4">
                <a class="my-4" href="/outreach">Outreach</a>
                <a class="my-4" href="/services">Services</a>
                <a class="my-4" href="/resources">Resources</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/events">Events</a>
        <div id="donate"><a href="/donate" >Donate</a></div>
    </div>
</nav>

<div id="donatePanel">
    <div id="black-box">
        <h1 class="text-center" id="display">Donate</h1>
        <div class="input-group">
            <span class="input-group-text">$</span>
            <input dir="rtl" type="number" class="form-control" placeholder="USD">
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between py-5">
            <button class="btn donateBtn" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#exampleModal"><h4>Once</h4></button>
            <button class="btn donateBtn" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#exampleModal"><h4>Monthly</h4></button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script type="text/javascript">
    function googleTranslateElementInit() {
        new google.translate.TranslateElement({pageLanguage: 'en', layout: google.translate.TranslateElement.InlineLayout.SIMPLE}, 'google_translate_element');
    }
</script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="//translate.google.com/translate_a/element.js?cb=googleTranslateElementInit"></script>

<div class="px-4" id="google_translate_element"></div>
<main class="container my-5">
    <div class="modal fade" id="exampleModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-xl">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">Donation</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    Look, we're gonna level with you... We are <strong>NOT</strong> the official Legal Services for Seniors website, this is a purely an educational project for Web Design. This website's purpose was to take a preexisting website and fix or improve the UI/UX experience. If you really want to donate to Legal Services for Seniors and help their cause, please go to <a href="https://www.lssmc.net">lssmc.net</a> and click on the donate button. If you are from Legal Services for Seniors and don't this website up, don't worry, the website will be taken down on May 24th, 2021. We just need this website up until we present it for our final grade.
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>
<footer class="container"><%- include("partials/footer") %></footer>
</body>
</html>